---
import Container from '../Container.astro';
---

<section id="capacidades" class="scroll-mt-20">
  <Container class="py-20 sm:py-28">
    <div class="max-w-2xl">
      <p class="font-mono text-[13px] uppercase tracking-widest text-fg-3">Capacidades</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-4xl">
        Cuatro capacidades, una sola plataforma
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-fg-2">
        Aurora aporta la base que todo sistema empresarial repite: cómo se crea un módulo, cómo
        habla con el núcleo, cómo opera en producción y cómo se gobierna su evolución. Make genera,
        el SDK conecta, el Runtime opera y la Architecture gobierna.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-6">
      <!-- Aurora Make (wide) -->
      <article
        class="group flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-line bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-line-2 hover:bg-panel-2 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-4"
      >
        <div
          class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-line bg-panel-2 text-brand-bright"
        >
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="10" cy="10" r="7.5"></circle>
            <path d="M2.5 10h15M10 2.5c2.4 2.6 2.4 12.4 0 15-2.4-2.6-2.4-12.4 0-15Z"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-[15px] font-semibold text-fg">Aurora Make — fábrica de módulos</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-2">
          Describa un módulo con un contrato estructurado — un <code class="font-mono text-[13px] text-fg">module.yaml</code> —
          y <code class="font-mono text-[13px] text-fg">aurora:make-module</code> genera los artefactos para
          integrarlo a la plataforma: modelos, migraciones, permisos y costuras de posteo, ya cableados.
          El manifiesto es la fuente de verdad; la lógica de dominio se escribe sobre el esqueleto.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <div class="divide-y divide-line rounded-lg border border-line font-mono text-[11px]">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">module.yaml</span>
              <span class="text-fg-3" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              <span class="text-fg-2">manifiesto declarativo</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">aurora:make-module</span>
              <span class="text-fg-3" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              <span class="text-fg-2">genera el paquete</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">Aurora\&lt;Module&gt;</span>
              <span class="text-fg-3" aria-hidden="true">→</span>
              <span class="text-fg-2">integrado, frontera limpia</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/aurora-make" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-fg-2 transition-colors hover:text-fg focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-brand">
          Conocer Aurora Make <span aria-hidden="true" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5">→</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Aurora Platform SDK (narrow) -->
      <article
        class="group flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-line bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-line-2 hover:bg-panel-2 lg:col-span-2"
      >
        <div
          class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-line bg-panel-2 text-brand-bright"
        >
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M7 5.5 2.5 10 7 14.5M13 5.5 17.5 10 13 14.5"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-[15px] font-semibold text-fg">Aurora Platform SDK — contratos estables</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-2">
          Un conjunto de contratos define cómo los módulos interactúan con el núcleo. Los módulos
          dependen de contratos, nunca de implementaciones concretas — el sistema evoluciona sin
          romper lo que ya existe.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <div class="divide-y divide-line rounded-lg border border-line font-mono text-[11px]">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">CreatesJournalEntries</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-fg-2">contrato</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">ResolvesTaxEffects</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-fg-2">contrato</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">ChecksStockAvailability</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-fg-2">contrato</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/aurora-platform-sdk" class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 pt-6 text-sm font-medium text-fg-2 transition-colors hover:text-fg focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-brand">
          Conocer el SDK <span aria-hidden="true" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5">→</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Aurora Runtime (wide) -->
      <article
        class="group flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-line bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-line-2 hover:bg-panel-2 sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-4"
      >
        <div
          class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-line bg-panel-2 text-brand-bright"
        >
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <circle cx="5.5" cy="4.5" r="2"></circle>
            <circle cx="5.5" cy="15.5" r="2"></circle>
            <circle cx="14.5" cy="6.5" r="2"></circle>
            <path d="M5.5 6.5v7M14.5 8.5c0 3.2-3.4 4-6.2 4.4"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-[15px] font-semibold text-fg">Aurora Runtime — infraestructura compartida</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-2">
          La capa donde los módulos se descubren, se registran y operan dentro del ecosistema.
          Incluye soporte multiempresa, onboarding, registries y componentes reutilizables — un
          módulo se enchufa y queda listo para operar.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap items-start gap-2 font-mono text-[11px]">
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-line px-3 py-1.5">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="text-fg-2">ModuleRegistry</span>
            <span class="text-fg-3">descubrimiento</span>
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-line px-3 py-1.5">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="text-fg-2">OnboardingRegistry</span>
            <span class="text-fg-3">readiness por empresa</span>
          </span>
          <span class="flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-line px-3 py-1.5">
            <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-accent" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            <span class="text-fg-2">multiempresa</span>
            <span class="text-fg-3">aislamiento por tenant</span>
          </span>
        </div>

        <a href="/aurora-runtime" class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm font-medium text-fg-2 transition-colors hover:text-fg focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-brand">
          Conocer Aurora Runtime <span aria-hidden="true" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5">→</span>
        </a>
      </article>

      <!-- Aurora Architecture (narrow) -->
      <article
        class="group flex flex-col rounded-xl border border-line bg-panel p-6 transition-colors hover:border-line-2 hover:bg-panel-2 lg:col-span-2"
      >
        <div
          class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-line bg-panel-2 text-brand-bright"
        >
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M2.5 10h3L8 4l4 12 2.5-6h3"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-4 text-[15px] font-semibold text-fg">Aurora Architecture — reglas verificadas</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-fg-2">
          Las decisiones de arquitectura, las fronteras entre módulos y los invariantes de negocio
          se registran en ADRs y se verifican automáticamente con fitness functions en cada build.
          La consistencia no se documenta: se comprueba.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-6">
          <div class="divide-y divide-line rounded-lg border border-line font-mono text-[11px]">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">ADR</span>
              <span class="text-fg-3">decisión registrada</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-accent">✓</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">frontera</span>
              <span class="text-fg-3">sin deps cruzadas</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-accent">✓</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-2">
              <span class="text-fg">invariante</span>
              <span class="text-fg-3">integridad financiera</span>
              <span class="ml-auto text-accent">✓</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <a href="/aurora-architecture" class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 pt-6 text-sm font-medium text-fg-2 transition-colors hover:text-fg focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-brand">
          Conocer Aurora Architecture <span aria-hidden="true" class="transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-0.5">→</span>
        </a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
